frames.caption: A magical scene depicts a tree made of golden butterflies, set against a cosmic backdrop. The butterflies appear to be in motion, fluttering around the twisted branches of the tree. The vibrant colors and ethereal setting create a sense of wonder and fantasy.
frames.description: The scene is set in a fantastical universe where a tree composed entirely of golden butterflies stands against a starry, cosmic sky. The butterflies are in various stages of flight, creating a dynamic and enchanting atmosphere.

frames.caption: A mystical tree with golden butterflies fluttering around it stands against a cosmic backdrop. The butterflies appear to be emerging from the tree, creating a magical and enchanting scene. The night sky is filled with stars, adding to the dreamlike atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal and magical setting where a tree is surrounded by numerous golden butterflies. The background is a cosmic night sky filled with stars, enhancing the fantastical and ethereal ambiance.
